  <brief_title>Influence of Hyaluronic Acid on Bacillus Calmette-Guérin Local Side Effects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study of Influence of Hyaluronic Acid (HA) on Bacillus Calmette-Guérin (BCG) Local Side Effects</official_title>
